"In this presentation, you will learn how you interact with standards every "
"day.  Then you will be introduced to https://www.tdwg.org/[Biodiversity "
"Information Standards^], including the https://www.tdwg.org/standards/dwc/"
"[Darwin Core Standard^] with which you will continue to use throughout this "
"course."
